  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ambalangoda shooting, one person in hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Ambalangoda Police, a person was seriously injured in a shooting that took place this afternoon (26th) at Gangarama Mawatha, Uravatta, Ambalangoda.",
        "Police say that Murukkuwadura Wasantha de Soyza, a resident of Ambalangoda Landthota, was injured in this shooting.",
        "The police also say that two unknown gunmen who came on a motorcycle shot at this person who was riding a motorcycle and fled.",
        "The police say that the person who was shot is a person who was released on bail after being remanded in custody for an incident of shooting at a person in Uravatta Parathandia area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda more than two years ago.",
        "The police suspect that this may be the result of collusion. Ambalangoda Police is conducting further investigations in this regard."
      ],
